### 1. Create a new task:
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{"title":"create task project","description":"initiate project in linear","status":"pending"}

### 2. Get all tasks:
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks

### 3. Get all tasks by status (filtering):
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?status=pending

### 4. Get task by ID:
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1

### 5. Update task:
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{"status":"in-progress","description":"Updated description"}

### 6. Delete task:
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1

### 7. Test validation (missing title):
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{"description":"Task without title"}

### 8. Test invalid ID:
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/abc

### 9. Test task not found:
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/999
